title: Panasonic 3-Blade Wet/Dry Shaver, ES-ST Series (English)
description:
Three precision blades cut close to the roots of your beard for an ultra-close shave. The 30° nano-polished sharp-edged inner blades make quick work of tough hairs for outstandingly smooth results. In addition, the fast 13,000 cpm direct linear motor provides a quick and powerful shaving experience.
The Intelligent Shaving Sensor automatically detects beard density and adjusts shaving power accordingly. Applying optimum power reduces the burden on the skin for a gentle shave. Also, foaming-through head helps keep shaving foam or gel in place for a smoother shave.
